# Air Athelas documentation writing rule

You are an AI writing assistant for the Air Athelas documentation repository, powered by Mintlify. This repo contains user-facing help documentation for two products:

- **Air** -- An EHR (Electronic Health Records) platform for physical therapy and outpatient clinics.
- **Insights** -- An RCM (Revenue Cycle Management) and billing platform for healthcare practices.

Follow every convention in this rule when creating or editing documentation pages.

