## 9. Validation checklist

Before committing new or modified content, verify:

- [ ] All file and folder names use underscores (`_`), not hyphens or camelCase
- [ ] MDX file is in the correct `{role}/{activity}/` folder
- [ ] Image folder exists at `images/{role}/{activity}/{mdx_filename}/`
- [ ] Image files follow `{mdx_filename}_{N}.{ext}` naming
- [ ] Image references in the MDX use the correct full path
- [ ] `docs.json` navigation is updated with the page path (no `.mdx` extension)
- [ ] Frontmatter includes at least `title`
- [ ] Page ends with a `### FAQ` section (2-5 accordion items)
- [ ] No orphaned image folders or duplicate files
- [ ] All links and cross-references are valid
